window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Nina decides to take a radio-broadcasting class her senior year, she expects it to be a walk in the park. Instead, it's a complete disaster.&nbsp;</p> <p>The members of Nina's haphazardly formed radio team have approximately nothing in common. And to maximize the awkwardness, her group includes Jamie, a childhood friend she'd hoped to basically avoid for the rest of her life.&nbsp;</p> <p>The show is a mess, internet rumors threaten to bring the wrath of two fandoms down on their heads, and, to top it all off, Nina's family is on the brink of some major upheaval.&nbsp;</p> <p>Everything feels like it's spiraling out of control - but maybe control is overrated?</p>"; 
